<item>
            <title>[LU-405] NFS4 reexport fails with ll_find_alias()) ASSERTION(last_discon == NULL)</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-405</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This is basically the same issue as bug 20055. NFS lookup path is quite different than that of normal VFS and as the result a number of disconnected dentries might appear on Lustre inode.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We probably jus tneed to have the same workaround as in 1.8 - to disable the assertion&lt;/p&gt;</description>
